en_584677_0	Speaker KaruJayasuriya has signed the Investigation Commission Amendment Act which was passed in Parliament.
en_584677_1	It will provide the opportunity to use commission reports as evidence.
en_584677_2	The Investigation Commission Amendment Act was passed in Parliament on the 22nd of this month.
en_584677_3	The Speaker signed the Act last evening empowering the Act.
en_584677_4	It will provide the opportunity to use evidence at the Investigation Commissions and the Commission to Investigate Bribery or Corruption.
en_584677_5	The Act will pave the way to speed up investigations.
